                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Home Delivery</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We offer convenient home delivery of medications and health products right to your doorstep.</p>
                <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-800">Learn More</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Service Card 5 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="flex justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-blue-600 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">24/7 Support</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Our team is available round the clock to assist you with any medical queries or emergencies.</p>
                <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-800">Learn More</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Service Card 6 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="flex justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-blue-600 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Health Records</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Manage and access your health records securely online for better healthcare management.</p>
                <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-800">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Call to Action Section -->
        <div class="bg-blue-50 mt-16 py-12">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Need Help Choosing a Service?</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Our team of experts is here to help you find the best services for your needs.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-300">Contact Us</a>
